column5: The NARDA Group will be hosting their 15th Annual "Wing Night" at Birch Dale Lodge on Eagle Lake, Saturday 8/22/15 at 7pm. If you are in the area stop by and have some wings and a drink or two!!
Going to see if i can make it.sounds like a blast
